node.text: Way To Go👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻Miss Lou & Daniel, ENJOY yourselves Today doing your “12-Hr Music Marathon” 👍🏻😊🙏🏻💕

𝟏𝟐-𝐇𝐎𝐔𝐑 𝐋𝐈𝐕𝐄 𝐒𝐓𝐑𝐄𝐀𝐌: 𝐌𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐜 & 𝐂𝐨𝐧𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 
This Saturday, 16 May, stay home and be entertained with music and conversations for 12 hours straight on YouTube!

Co-anchored by saxophonist Daniel Chia (@danielchiaofficial) and myself, the 12-hour program will be hosted on Daniel Chia’s YouTube channel, and will feature international guests dialing in LIVE from the US, Taiwan, Thailand, and Singapore.

Join us as we keep you company for the whole of Saturday! Link in bio!

𝙎𝙘𝙝𝙚𝙙𝙪𝙡𝙚 𝙖𝙣𝙙 𝙡𝙞𝙣𝙚-𝙪𝙥:
10am - Daniel Chia + Miss Lou
11am - Adam Hawley @adamhawleymusic, US Billboard Chart-Topping Guitarist & Producer
12pm - Daniel Chia
1pm - Kevin Foo @kevinfoomusic, General Manager of Sony Music Taiwan
2pm - Miss Lou
3pm - Grace Fu @gracefu.hy, Minister for Culture, Community, and Youth
4pm - Joanna Dong @j_o_a_n_n_a_d_o_n_g, Jazz Vocalist & TV Presenter
5pm - Koh Mr. Saxman @kohmrsaxman, Thailand’s Premier Saxophonist
6pm - Daniel Chia + Miss Lou
7pm - Aisyah Aziz @aisyaah_aziz, R&B Songstress & Actress
8pm - Joshua Simon @joshuasimonxl, Independent Music Artist & Radio DJ
9pm - Daniel Chia + Miss Lou

#SGUnited #StayHomeSG
